<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>HTML Links and Image Map Example</title>

<style>
body{
font-family: Arial;
background-color:#f2f2f2;
margin:20px;
}

h1{
color:#2c3e50;
}

a{
color:blue;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
}

a:hover{
color:red;
}

img{
border-radius:8px;
}

.section{
background:white;
padding:15px;
margin-bottom:20px;
border-radius:10px;
box-shadow:0px 0px 10px gray;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<center>
<h1>HTML Links and Image Map Example</h1>
</center>

<hr>

<div class="section">

<h2>1. Text Link Example</h2>

<p>
<a href="https://www.google.com" target="_blank">
Visit Google Website
</a>
</p>

<p>
<a href="https://www.github.com" target="_blank">
Open GitHub
</a>
</p>

</div>

<div class="section">

<h2>2. Image Link Example</h2>

<a href="https://www.wikipedia.org" target="_blank">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/63/Wikipedia-logo.png" width="120">
</a>

<p>Click the Wikipedia logo to open the website.</p>

</div>

<div class="section">

<h2>3. Image as a Link</h2>

<a href="https://www.youtube.com" target="_blank">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b8/YouTube_Logo_2017.svg" width="200">
</a>

<p>Click the YouTube logo.</p>

</div>

<div class="section">

<h2>4. Image Map Example</h2>

<p>Click different areas of the workspace image.</p>

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517336714731-489689fd1ca8"
width="700" height="400" usemap="#workmap">

<map name="workmap">

<!-- Laptop -->
<area shape="rect"
coords="50,120,350,330"
href="https://www.wikipedia.org"
target="_blank"
alt="Laptop">

<!-- Notebook -->
<area shape="rect"
coords="380,150,520,330"
href="https://www.google.com"
target="_blank"
alt="Notebook">

<!-- Phone -->
<area shape="rect"
coords="540,160,630,310"
href="https://www.github.com"
target="_blank"
alt="Phone">

<!-- Coffee Cup -->
<area shape="circle"
coords="600,80,40"
href="https://www.youtube.com"
target="_blank"
alt="Coffee Cup">

</map>

</div>

<div class="section">

<h2>5. Workspace Image</h2>

<p>This image shows a modern workspace.</p>

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492724441997-5dc865305da7" width="700">

</div>

<hr>

<center>
<p>HTML Practice Program - Links and Image Map</p>
</center>

</body>
</html>
